<p>To <a href="https://securenest.org/learn/advanced-solana-development">optimize your Solana dApp for performance</a> and scalability, focus on efficient code, minimize network calls, utilize parallel processing, and leverage Solana&#8217;s built-in features like transaction batching and program optimization.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Security Considerations Should I Take Into Account Before Launching My Solana dApp?</h3>



<p>Before launching your Solana dApp, it&#8217;s essential to consider security. Protect sensitive user data, implement strong authentication measures, conduct thorough code audits, and stay informed about the latest security vulnerabilities to ensure a secure deployment.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Are the Best Practices for Writing and Testing Robust Smart Contracts on Solana?</h3>



